data.description: Experience Simplified Living! Dive into the luxury of one-level living with this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem nestled within a prestigious golf course location. The ideal home for those valuing convenience with a spacious layout and an attached double garage that's perfect for vehicles or additional storage. Dreaming of serene winters without the hassle of snow removal? It's time to retire your shovels and snowblowers, as the HOA is dedicated to making your life effortless, handling all seasonal maintenance for you. While the home's interiors are a canvas of potential with a need for new flooring, it offers an exciting opportunity to customize it to your taste and elevate its charm. Don't let this chance slip away. Call today for your own private showing and envision the possibilities of 1 level living.
